("film-looks-grades","16mm Film Look","Grainy, slightly soft small-gauge film texture; indie warmth and imperfection.","Use for memory sequences, music videos, and handmade honesty.","\"16mm film look, summer lake, grain and halation\"","analog;handheld"),
("film-looks-grades","Technicolor","Vintage three-strip saturation: reds that sing, greens that glow, Hollywood's candy era.","Use for retro musicals, dream sequences, and joyful artifice.","\"1950s kitchen, technicolor grade\"","high-key-lighting;jewel-tones"),
